s/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"三十幾就出得院"},{"pid":"e1e86308c535e612d2c60449adab521d79f88437","tid":2424162,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"754e24c7cb07d2db8408f9f4933f61e57cab1576","tid":2424162,"uid":7416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:17:29.000Z","msg":"病毒CT值18 其實個數可以去到幾大 點為之多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"ct值係指放大幾多倍至睇到,全名叫做「cycle threshold」<br />\n<br />\n從台灣究中，直接採樣病人檢體培養，證實Ct值35.2，過去醫檢單位也發現，確診者Ct值有時確實會超過35，施信如指出，Ct值與確診關係可分三層次，Ct值30以下即確診、30至35也視為確診，至於35以上、40以下，則建議採檢第二次，改以血清抗體、基因檢測綜合判斷。"},{"pid":"8545c81e94cd3643edd5352d6f3daca88500599b","tid":2424162,"uid":36567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f8ff4c82c2e1493e5389313022822419b6dbe36c","tid":2424162,"uid":189,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"做檢測<br />\n用安心出行<br />\n打疫苗<br />\n<br />\n藍絲三寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"打疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打支那疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你首先要明白呢個世界上有兩種疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebf40f35a144c160b875facb950f977e4b9af2b","tid":2424162,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"笑撚到我仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98db0ddb9521d49145b604